# InferTest — expected entailments
# Construct : owl:someValuesFrom (existential restriction)

@prefix : <http://example.org/infertest#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .

### Pat has a child (Sam) who is a Person -> Pat satisfies the existential
### restriction and must be typed Parent.
:SomeValuesFrom_Pat rdf:type :SomeValuesFrom_Parent .
